    <div n="1.38">
<l n="1"><rs type ="ethnic" urn="urn:cite2:hmt:ls.markdown:n35436">Persicos</rs> odi, puer, apparatus,</l>
<l n="2">displicent nexae philyra coronae,</l>
<l n="3">mitte sectari, rosa quo locorum</l>
<l n="4">sera moretur.</l>
<l n="5">Simplici myrto nihil adlabores</l>
<l n="6">sedulus, curo: neque te ministrum</l>
<l n="7">dedecet myrtus neque me sub arta</l>
<l n="8">vite bibentem.</l>
    </div>
